- `ui/backend/services/render/field_sample.py:_atomic_write_guarded`
- `ui/backend/services/render/geometry_glb.py:_atomic_write_guarded`
- `ui/backend/services/render/mesh_wireframe.py:_atomic_write_guarded_multi`

If clean: APPROVE or APPROVE_WITH_COMMENTS.

